features: 3-Piece Maple Leaf Cookie Cutters Set, Available in three sizes: 4.1'', 3.3'' And 2.2''
Manufactured with certified food safe steel. All cutters have a thinner cutting edge to ensure a cleaner cut in your cookie dough.
Makes excellent cookies with these durable and beautiful fall Leaves cookie cutters.

Red Top Cookie Cutters: The top edge of the cookie cutters is wrapped in food-grade PVC material, making it easy to tell the front and back of the cookie cutters, while protecting your fingers as you use them.
The maple leaf cookie cutters are made of sturdy and durable 0.4mm materials, ensure they will last for a long time and you don't have to worry about your child bending them out of shape.
